ABC, ABCTV, AUSTRALIAN, TV, DRAMA, COMEDY, SERIES
CREATED BY: John Misto, STARS: Aaron Blabey, Monica Maughan, Philip Quast 

When Harvey McHugh tries to get a permanent government job, he undertakes an epic journey through the corridors of power. On the way, this innocent young clerk gains an alarming insight into how the country is run from his dealings with a corrupt politician.

Funny, poignant and a theme very relevant worldwide, Harvey McHugh is a morality tale about life and government in modern times.
